Detailed Description

cvmx_tim_ring::_ctl0

Notes: This CSR is a memory of 64 entries After a 1 to 0 transition on ENA, the HW will still complete a bucket traversal for the ring if it was pending or active prior to the transition. (SW must delay to ensure the completion of the traversal before reprogramming the ring.)
